attributeValues.value: Style&co.'s straight-leg pants are a seasonless staple for any work wardrobe! The pull-on style and tummy-control design make this a closet must-have.
Mid rise: waistband sits below natural waist
Approximate model measurements: height: 5'10"; bust: 35.5"; waist: 27"; hips: 35"
Faux pockets at front; welt pockets at back
Generous sizing; if in-between sizes, consider sizing down
Returns are accepted at any Macy's store within 180 days from purchase date. Last Act items must be returned within 30 days from purchase date.
